Package: regin
Version: 0.1.0
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.35)
Maintainer: exedev <exedev@driessel.exe.xyz>
Description: AI-powered monitoring and audit agent
 Named after the dwarf smith from the Sigurd saga.
 Regin runs scheduled monitoring "skills" (markdown-defined tasks)
 through an LLM and provides an interactive chat interface.
 .
 Includes two binaries:
  - regind: systemd daemon for scheduled skill execution
  - regin: CLI with interactive chat and skill management
